===Noun===
[[Image:Badger.png|thumbnail|right|A badger]]
'''badger''' (''plural'' [[badgers]])

# Any of several carnivorous burrowing [[animal]]s in the family ''Mustelidae''.
# A native or resident of the State of [[Wisconsin]] (US).
# ''plural'' {{vulgar}} (''cant'') A crew of desperate villains who robbed near rivers, into which they threw the bodies of those they murdered.
# A person who makes [http://www.weebadgers.com badges].

